pdb-fixer (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * Add an offline Nuitka executable for repairing PDB structures.
  * Replace nonstandard residues.
  * Optionally add missing residues, missing atoms, and hydrogens.

